Actions.Title: Spotlight Search
Actions.ActionName: Tell the user we need them to locate the resources package for us.
Actions.Prompt:
You need to specify the location of the Resources package "Spotlight Search Prompt Resources.pkg".

Please click "OK", and locate the Resources package.

Actions.ActionName: Have the user pick the resources package
Actions.Text: tell application (path to frontmost application as text)	set dir to POSIX path of (choose file with prompt "Please locate the file 'Spotlight Search Prompt Resources.pkg'")end tell
